---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "Need of accessible car for muscular dystrophy";
const metaDescription =
  "Why accessible cars are essential for muscular dystrophy: independence, safety, and key accessible features.";
const currentSlug = "need-of-accessible-car-for-muscular-dystrophy";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">February 13, 2023 · by vivek · 1 Comment</p>
      <h1>Need of accessible car for muscular dystrophy</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>
          Muscular dystrophy is a group of genetic diseases that cause progressive muscle weakness and loss. As the
          disease progresses, people with muscular dystrophy may find it increasingly difficult to walk, climb stairs, and
          get in and out of cars. This can make it difficult to maintain independence and participate in activities that
          they enjoy.
        </p>

        <h2>Why an Accessible Car is Important</h2>
        <p>An accessible car can make a big difference in the life of someone with muscular dystrophy. An accessible car can provide the following benefits:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Increased independence: An accessible car can help people with muscular dystrophy to maintain their independence by making it easier for them to get around.</li>
          <li>Improved safety: An accessible car can help to improve safety by making it easier for people with muscular dystrophy to get in and out of the car and by providing features that can help them to drive safely.</li>
          <li>Improved quality of life: An accessible car can help to improve the quality of life for people with muscular dystrophy by giving them the freedom to travel and participate in activities that they enjoy.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Types of Accessible Cars</h2>
        <p>
          There are a variety of accessible cars available, including cars that are wheelchair accessible and cars that
          have features that make it easier for people with limited mobility to get in and out of the car. Some of the
          features that may be found in an accessible car include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Wide entryways: Wide entryways make it easier for people with mobility impairments to get in and out of the car.</li>
          <li>Power-operated seats: Power-operated seats can help people with limited mobility to get in and out of the car more easily.</li>
          <li>Hand controls: Hand controls allow people with limited mobility to drive the car using their hands.</li>
          <li>Wheelchair ramps: Wheelchair ramps allow people who use wheelchairs to get in and out of the car more easily.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Buying an Accessible Car</h2>
        <p>True Assistive Tech flagship product “Turn Plus” can convert your existing car to be accessible car.</p>

        <h2>Conclusion</h2>
        <p>
          An accessible car can make a big difference in the life of someone with muscular dystrophy. By providing
          increased independence, improved safety, and improved quality of life, an accessible car can help people with
          muscular dystrophy to maintain their independence and participate in activities that they enjoy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/swivel-seat" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="product-image">
              <img src="https://www.trueassistech.com/assets/images/products/swivel-seat.jpg" alt="Swivel Seat product" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">Swivel Seat</p>
              <p class="product-link">Assisted swivel entry and exit.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/wheelchair-ramp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="product-image">
              <img src="https://www.trueassistech.com/assets/images/products/wheelchair-ramp.jpg" alt="Wheelchair ramp product" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">Wheelchair Ramps</p>
              <p class="product-link">Portable ramps for smooth entry.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(69, 30, 93, 0.08), rgba(69, 30, 93, 0.03));
  }

  .product-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>


